Born on a cold seafloor, it
will swim great distances to
return to its birthplace.

Water makes up 80% of its body.
This Pokémon is easily affected by
its environment.

It is born with a wondrous power
that lets it bond with any kind of
Pokémon.

that permits it to bond with any kind

ふしぎな　ちからを　つかうと　どんな
ポケモンとも　こころが　かよいあう。

태어났을 때부터 가지고 있는
이상한 힘을 쓰면 어떤 포켓몬과도
마음이 서로 통하게 된다.

Il est né avec le pouvoir incroyable de créer des liens
avec n’importe quel Pokémon.

Es wird mit einer wundersamen Kraft geboren,
die eine Bindung zu jedem anderen Pokémon
möglich macht.

Nace con un maravilloso poder que le permite
establecer vínculos con cualquier tipo de Pokémon.

Dispone di un potere innato che lo fa legare con
qualsiasi specie di Pokémon.

It is born with a wondrous power that lets it bond

ポケモンとも　心が　通い合う。

どんな　ポケモンとでも　こころを
